# apps/backend/src/modules/customer/

## Responsibility
Provides customer list/detail/update, stats, consent, tagging, and customer-level routing views.

## Design
Query-heavy service with flexible sorting/filtering and derived customer level definitions/mappings based on lifetime value and order totals.

## Flow
Routes fetch scoped lists, stats, level settings/preview, and edit customer/profile/tag data. Service maps contacts into DTOs and enriches with analytics.

## Integration
Uses Prisma, BusinessWebhookDispatchService, conversation/order data, and chatbot routing mappings for level-based automation.

